WEBVTT

00:00:00.075 --> 00:00:35.166
Subtitle Provide by dramacool.asia Translator [Admin.@YNG]

00:01:00.416 --> 00:01:01.333
Stay back.

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:07.125
You fiend.

00:01:07.291 --> 00:01:09.291
How dare you use an imposter to pose as my wife.

00:01:09.500 --> 00:01:10.791
Give me back my wife.

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:13.791
There is no Lady Shen.

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:16.000
It was fake from the very beginning.

00:01:17.208 --> 00:01:18.833
From the start,

00:01:19.500 --> 00:01:21.666
it was all your scheme.

00:01:22.125 --> 00:01:23.791
You are truly vicious.

00:01:25.875 --> 00:01:28.750
You have only yourself to blame for your uncontrollable desires.

00:01:29.166 --> 00:01:30.791
I placed someone by your side at random,

00:01:30.833 --> 00:01:32.583
and you fell for it so easily.

00:01:33.708 --> 00:01:35.083
Didn't you say

00:01:35.250 --> 00:01:37.791
you would give up everything for your wife?

00:01:38.083 --> 00:01:38.833
So,

00:01:39.125 --> 00:01:40.500
when you found out she didn't love you,

00:01:40.750 --> 00:01:42.208
you abandoned her?

00:01:45.708 --> 00:01:46.791
Lord Ghost King,

00:01:47.791 --> 00:01:49.125
why don't we make another wager?

00:01:49.833 --> 00:01:51.708
Let's bet if, besides your husband,

00:01:51.791 --> 00:01:53.291
there is a better man in this world.

00:01:53.708 --> 00:01:54.791
If there is,

00:01:56.791 --> 00:01:57.833
you let us go.

00:01:58.000 --> 00:01:59.041
How about it?

00:02:01.375 --> 00:02:02.875
What tricks are you planning now?

00:02:02.916 --> 00:02:03.750
We're all on your turf.

00:02:03.791 --> 00:02:05.000
What tricks could we possibly play?

00:02:06.333 --> 00:02:07.458
What are we betting on?

00:02:14.833 --> 00:02:17.000
Let's bet on Shen Wanyan and his wife.

00:02:20.708 --> 00:02:21.500
Fine.

00:02:22.250 --> 00:02:23.250
What's your proposal?

00:02:23.875 --> 00:02:25.208
Lord Ghost King, take a guess.

00:02:25.833 --> 00:02:28.583
If Shen Wanyan knew Lady Shen would surely die now,

00:02:29.333 --> 00:02:30.666
would he risk his life to save her?

00:02:31.166 --> 00:02:34.125
Lady Shen was just a venomous thorn I planted by his side.

00:02:34.333 --> 00:02:35.583
She was meant to lure him in.

00:02:36.333 --> 00:02:37.833
Now that he knows the truth,

00:02:38.125 --> 00:02:39.416
he surely won't save her.

00:02:40.333 --> 00:02:41.166
Very well.

00:02:41.916 --> 00:02:43.791
If the two of them can be like me,

00:02:44.000 --> 00:02:45.458
and my husband,

00:02:45.583 --> 00:02:47.208
become devoted lovers,

00:02:47.583 --> 00:02:49.541
I would be willing to let them be together.

00:02:52.083 --> 00:02:53.875
Bring her in.

00:02:55.500 --> 00:02:56.458
Lord Ghost King.

00:02:56.541 --> 00:02:57.375
My lady.

00:02:58.500 --> 00:02:59.791
Kill him.

00:03:02.458 --> 00:03:03.833
Since this is a game,

00:03:03.958 --> 00:03:04.916
the rules

00:03:05.250 --> 00:03:06.708
will be set by me.

00:03:07.208 --> 00:03:08.458
Shen Wanyan,

00:03:09.291 --> 00:03:10.500
listen carefully.

00:03:10.916 --> 00:03:13.125
Your wife was never dead.

00:03:13.375 --> 00:03:14.500
In this world,

00:03:14.625 --> 00:03:16.666
there is no such thing as resurrection.

00:03:17.333 --> 00:03:19.875
The one you spent your fortune to save

00:03:20.041 --> 00:03:23.000
was just a venomous thorn I placed by your side.

00:03:23.458 --> 00:03:25.291
She never loved you.

00:03:28.666 --> 00:03:31.750
Today, between you and her,

00:03:32.041 --> 00:03:34.291
only one can leave here alive.

00:03:34.375 --> 00:03:36.333
If you can kill her with your own hands,

00:03:36.416 --> 00:03:38.666
I will let you and the others go.

00:04:17.833 --> 00:04:19.166
See?

00:04:19.541 --> 00:04:21.250
Men in this world

00:04:21.875 --> 00:04:24.333
are all heartless and unfaithful.

00:04:35.583 --> 00:04:36.708
My lady,

00:04:38.500 --> 00:04:40.125
I actually knew long ago

00:04:41.583 --> 00:04:43.500
that maybe you were deceiving me.

00:04:46.333 --> 00:04:47.500
But I understand

00:04:48.166 --> 00:04:49.708
as a woman,

00:04:50.625 --> 00:04:53.458
how hard it is to survive.

00:04:56.333 --> 00:04:57.500
So I thought,

00:04:59.541 --> 00:05:01.291
even if this is all fake,

00:05:02.000 --> 00:05:03.291
so what?

00:05:05.000 --> 00:05:06.291
As long as I can

00:05:08.625 --> 00:05:10.583
love you a little longer,

00:05:12.291 --> 00:05:14.958
I can protect you a little longer.

00:05:17.875 --> 00:05:19.250
But now,

00:05:21.208 --> 00:05:23.458
I canâ€™t protect you anymore.

00:05:27.500 --> 00:05:28.916
I have to go.

00:05:36.250 --> 00:05:37.208
Shen Wanyan! Shen Wanyan!

00:05:37.250 --> 00:05:38.041
Shen Wanyan!

00:05:44.583 --> 00:05:46.500
Wanyan...

00:05:52.541 --> 00:05:53.291
Wanyan...

00:05:53.333 --> 00:05:54.416
Lady Shen,

00:05:55.208 --> 00:05:56.875
Shen Wanyan loves you so deeply.

00:05:56.916 --> 00:05:58.666
He would even give up his life for you.

00:05:59.166 --> 00:06:01.041
Have you never loved him?

00:06:01.375 --> 00:06:02.333
Wanyan...

00:06:41.166 --> 00:06:42.041
Lady

00:06:42.625 --> 00:06:44.791
I will find a way to save you.

00:06:48.166 --> 00:06:49.666
She is my wife.

00:07:43.541 --> 00:07:44.833
What a pity.

00:07:48.833 --> 00:07:50.125
Kill them.

00:07:50.583 --> 00:07:51.500
Nobody move.

00:07:51.708 --> 00:07:52.375
Hurry!

00:07:52.583 --> 00:07:53.541
Quick!

00:07:55.458 --> 00:07:57.750
Capture all these monsters and demons!

00:07:59.291 --> 00:08:00.166
Godfather.

00:08:00.250 --> 00:08:01.500
This person

00:08:01.750 --> 00:08:04.166
is the Jinwu Guard Lieutenant.

00:08:04.375 --> 00:08:06.166
Please secretly follow me when the time comes.

00:08:06.250 --> 00:08:08.291
If we don't return with the suspect in two hours,

00:08:08.333 --> 00:08:09.583
send the Jinwu Guard to attack.

00:08:09.666 --> 00:08:11.833
The Jinwu Guard will follow Chief Li's orders.

00:08:25.208 --> 00:08:26.208
Husband,

00:08:27.291 --> 00:08:29.291
I can't help you anymore.

00:08:57.041 --> 00:08:59.166
Stop shaking, you're making me dizzy.

00:09:01.458 --> 00:09:02.916
Although the case is closed,

00:09:03.125 --> 00:09:04.625
there are still unsolved mysteries.

00:09:04.791 --> 00:09:06.291
I suspect Sheng Li's death

00:09:06.958 --> 00:09:08.625
is hiding a bigger conspiracy.

00:09:08.791 --> 00:09:09.958
But with her death,

00:09:10.125 --> 00:09:11.541
all the clues are gone.

00:09:12.875 --> 00:09:14.666
Aren't you the Deputy Chief of the Unsolved Cases Bureau?

00:09:14.791 --> 00:09:17.208
Isn't their goal just to make you a puppet?

00:09:18.416 --> 00:09:19.250
Do you think this

00:09:19.291 --> 00:09:21.541
is connected to the court's conspiracy?

00:09:22.916 --> 00:09:23.958
Didn't you

00:09:24.041 --> 00:09:25.625
send someone to investigate Sheng Li's background,

00:09:25.666 --> 00:09:27.000
to find out who her husband was?

00:09:27.250 --> 00:09:28.041
Why haven't they returned yet?

00:09:28.041 --> 00:09:28.875
Boss.

00:09:29.333 --> 00:09:30.041
Boss.

00:09:30.416 --> 00:09:31.208
Boss.

00:09:31.375 --> 00:09:32.208
I've found out

00:09:32.375 --> 00:09:34.833
Sheng Li did have a husband before.

00:09:35.625 --> 00:09:36.541
He's not dead.

00:09:36.791 --> 00:09:38.166
He's still alive.

00:09:40.125 --> 00:09:42.125
Who is he? Tell us!

00:09:43.750 --> 00:09:44.541
This person

00:09:44.708 --> 00:09:45.708
is

00:09:45.875 --> 00:09:47.291
Eunuch Qiu.